0.0.6 2019-09-10
    - [LibXML::Native] Change cglobals from constants to subs (avoid compilation failures #16)
    - [LibXML::Native::Defs] rename library constants LIB -> XML2, BIND-LIB -> BIND-XML2; add CLIB for windows.
0.0.5 2019-09-08
    - [LibXML::Reader]
